source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000010_NALDTHAL<tab>I am Nald, keeper of the realm of the living.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000010_NALDTHAL<tab>私はナル！  生を司る神なり！

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000020_NALDTHAL<tab>I am Thal, keeper of the realm of the dead.
TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000025_NALDTHAL<tab>Prepare to be judged, children of man.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000025_NALDTHAL<tab>汝ら  人の力を裁定いたそう

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000040_ENDSINGER_NONE_VOICE<tab>Hope, is it...? Futile. Utterly futile.
Such feeble light is powerless before darkest despair.
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000040_ENDSINGER_NONE_VOICE<tab>祈りの力  希望の光か――
そんなものは  この暗き底へ  届きはしない！
